{"tid":2514031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"首爾直擊｜國產大使夫人發難摑人 女售貨員夫：妻遭拍後腦致耳鳴 拒大使沒誠意道歉","createTime":"2021-05-03T03:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T03:55:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef7fe8490cb3c4a0afe32258fd754f9b3dbd4c6","tid":2514031,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:52:41.000Z","msg":"南韓首爾女店員遭比利時駐韓大使的中國籍夫人掌摑而引發的外交風波，至今將近一個月，除大使代妻在Facebook道歉外，涉案女主角、太極高手相雪秋，事後聲稱中風入院，至今仍未公開露面。據悉，大使夫人已在上月23日出院。《蘋果》特約記者日前到訪事發服裝店，遇襲的女店員正受耳鳴及情緒困擾，無法受訪，但其丈夫對《蘋果》表示，妻子除受大使夫人掌摑外，後腦亦遭拍打，他批評大使的道歉「缺乏誠意」，不是大使夫人親自道歉，他們不會接受。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210503/EZ36NWE3ERGVRCRY5IUOX542UA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210503%2FEZ36NWE3ERGVRCRY5IUOX542UA%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=36aedc99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210503%2FEZ36NWE3ERGVRCRY5IUOX542UA%2F&h=0baaedfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210503/EZ36NWE3ERGVRCRY5IUOX542UA/</a>"},{"pid":"1f44dd257052f2cfdda8cc45a10fa1031ad8adc5","tid":2514031,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:55:21.000Z","msg":"狗改不了食屎"}]}